headline: Bitcoin and Ethereum ETFs roar back adding nearly $3bn last week
summary: Bitcoin and Ethereum ETFs brought in nearly $3 billion last week. Markets expect rate cuts, fueling crypto appetite. Ethereum has outperformed Bitcoin with 200% gains since April.

headline: Coinbase Hacker Is Betting on Ethereum – ETH Breakout?
summary: Ethereum (ETH) has a strong advocate in the hacker who attacked customers of American cryptocurrency exchange Coinbase a while ago. According to on-chain data, the crypto wallet linked to the hacker recently bought 3,976 Ethereum, worth more than $18.9 million. Markedly, the ETH was acquired at $4,756 per token. Series ...
